<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to InstaShare!</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <style>
      footer {
        position: fixed;
        padding: 10px 10px 0px 10px;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 80px;
        background: grey;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('_navbarLP') %>

    <header class="bg-primary text-white text-center py-5">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to InstaShare!</h1>
        <p class="lead">InstaShare is an online community dedicated to sharing precious moments in your life with friends, family, and the world. Join us today.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-5">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Main Features of InstaShare:</h2>
            <ol>
              <li>Share Precious Moments: Upload your photos and videos and let the world see them. Share your journeys, adventures, memories with friends, and other precious moments with ease.</li>
              <li>Explore the World: Find inspiration from various content shared by InstaShare users from around the world. Follow your favorite accounts and connect with new people.</li>
              <li>Deep Interactions: Like, comment, and interact with content from your friends. InstaShare allows you to connect with loved ones and those who share your interests.</li>
              <li>Security and Privacy: We prioritize the security and privacy of our users. Control who can view your content and manage privacy settings easily.</li>
              <li>Endless Exploration: Discover exciting content through hashtag searches and specific topics. Find content that matches your interests.</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-5">
            <br /><br /><br />
            <p class="lead">Join the InstaShare community today and start sharing moments, building relationships, and creating unforgettable memories.</p>
            <p>Make InstaShare your place to share stories, connect with others, and capture every beautiful moment in your life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-light py-4 text-center">
      <div class="container">
        <p>&copy; 2023 InstaShare. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

